Module frogger
Package frogger.model

Class Frog

java.lang.Object
javafx.scene.Node
javafx.scene.image.ImageView
frogger.model.Actor
frogger.model.Frog
All Implemented Interfaces:
javafx.css.Styleable, javafx.event.EventTarget
public class Frog
extends Actor
The most important element in the game. The Frog can jump around and interact with other game elements, leading a possible change to the game score.
